NG0456:1: rdo la gser du grub pa'o //
NG0456:2: gser 'dod rdo la re ba med //
NG0456:3: zhen pa ma chod bde ba yang *//
NG0456:4: zhen med ngo bor thongs pa med //
NG0456:5: 'dzin pa du ma rang grol na //
NG0456:6: yang dag rtsol bas sgrub tu med //
NG0456:7: rtsol med don la gnas pa ni //
NG0456:8: byang chub lag tu gtod pa yin //
NG0456:9: spong len med pa'i snang ba rang sol //
NG0456:10: dbus mtha' ma gzigs rnam par rtog dang bral //
NG0456:11: ye shes rnam dag lhun grub chen po la //
NG0456:12: re dogs med pas chos nyid rang la gsal //
NG0456:13: ye nas lhun grub sangs rgyas mngon gyur na //
NG0456:14: gang nas kun la sangs rgyas re ba med //
NG0456:15: sangs rgyas nyid kyis sangs rgyas nyid tshol ba //
NG0456:16: dper na ri dwags smig sgyu snyeg pa 'dra //
NG0456:17: des na sangs rgyas re dogs gzhan na med //
NG0456:18: dbye gsal blang dor med pa'i lung *//
NG0456:19: chos nyid ye nas rnam dag la //
NG0456:20: 'khor ba'i rnam rtog blang dor yul sbangs nas //
NG0456:21: snang la zhen med gar bder sbyod pa'i mchog / theg chen nam mkha'i dbyings na nyi ma shar //
NG0456:22: gdul bya gang zag rnams kyis don du snang *//
NG0456:23: don dam ngang la 'dul dang mi 'dul med //
NG0456:24: rig pa'i rgyal po ye shes nyi zer ni //
NG0456:25: mtha' yas sems can thams cad la //
NG0456:26: snang gsal sgron ma rtogs par shog / ye shais 'khor lo gsang ba'i rgyu las //
NG0456:27: rtsol bral thugs rje'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o ///
NG0456:28: / de nas rig pa'i rgyal pos //
NG0456:29: rdo rje sems dpa' la bka' stsal pa //
NG0456:30: rang snang rig pa'i ye shes la //
NG0456:31: ma rtogs bdud kyi spyod yul ni //
NG0456:32: stong pa byang chub lta ba'i bdud //
NG0456:33: had po bogs med sgom pa'i bdud //
NG0456:34: rtog med rang dga' spyod pa'i bdud //
NG0456:36: phra mos chog shes thos pa'i bdud //
NG0456:38: grub mtha' log pa chos kyi bdud /
NG0456:39: mi thub dam bca' dam tshig bdud //
NG0456:40: rim pa bsgrod pa dbang gi bdud //
NG0456:42: bar dor snang ba 'od kyi bdud //
NG0456:43: grags pa brgyad po dgra yi bdud //
NG0456:44: rnam rtogs 'phrin po nyid kyis bdud //
NG0456:45: kha shags don la bred pa'i bdud //
NG0456:46: mkhas pa mdo med shes rab bdud //
NG0456:47: rtog 'dzin zhes pa bag chags bdud //
NG0456:48: rang rig 'khrul par snang ba yi snang ba sna tshogs 'khrul pa'i bdud //
NG0456:49: thams cad bdud snang shes tsam na /
NG0456:50: bdud las nges par grol ba yin //
NG0456:51: ma rtogs pa ni bdud yin te //
NG0456:52: rtogs na bdud kyi rtsi ru 'gyur //
NG0456:53: dug la sman du shes pa bzhin //
NG0456:54: de las gzhan du shes mi 'gyur //
NG0456:55: ye shes 'khor lo gsang ba'i rgyud las //
NG0456:56: bdud kyi le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o ///
NG0456:57: / de nas rig pa'i rgyal bka' rtsal pa //
NG0456:58: lta ba bdag tu 'dzin pas gol //
NG0456:59: nga yis rang bzhin bcu po las //
NG0456:60: gol sa sgrib pa drug drug bcu //
NG0456:61: sum brgya drug cu phrag yas so //
NG0456:64: gang gis de rtogs de yi sras //
NG0456:65: lam ni rnam pa lnga dag kyang *//
NG0456:66: sa bcu bgrod pas gol pa'i lam //
NG0456:67: gdod nas ma skyes snying po la //
NG0456:68: tha tshig ming du btags pas gol //
NG0456:69: rang bzhin lhun grub chen po la //
NG0456:70: 'phrin las rnam bzhi dod nas rdzogs /
NG0456:71: bag chags rmi lam bsdu brid dang *//
NG0456:72: rigs drug gzugs sgra'i bsdu brid dang *//
NG0456:74: 'drin pa'i thabs dgu ngang la rdzogs //
NG0456:75: bag chag nying 'tshams sbyar ba dang *//
NG0456:76: sems nyid nying 'tshams sbyar ba dang *//
NG0456:77: phung po nying 'tshams sbyor ba gsum //
NG0456:78: nga yi rang bzhin rnams gsum yin //
NG0456:79: nga yi rang snang chen po rgyud //
NG0456:80: theg pa kun gyi la zlo ba //
NG0456:81: chos rnams mdangs skyel ba yi //
NG0456:83: 'khor gyi nang na dam pa ste //
NG0456:84: rdo rje sems dpa' khyod pa gtad //
NG0456:85: khyod ni mi nu stobs dang ldan //
NG0456:86: nga las mi gzhan 'khor yin pas //
NG0456:87: thugs kyi dkyil du mnyam par zhog / thugs rje'i gser ka phyogs bcur 'char //
NG0456:88: lan cig snyigs ma lnga dus na //
NG0456:89: nyi zla bzhin du dar bar shog / nam mkha' khyab pa'i 'jig rten du //
NG0456:90: sgron ma bzhin du rgyas par shog / 'khor ba ldongs pa'i mun pa rnams //
NG0456:91: ye shes 'od kyis gang bar shog / rgyud drug 'khrul pa'i sems can rnams //
NG0456:92: sangs rgyas sa la grol bar shog / ces gsungs so //
NG0456:93: ye shes 'khor lo gsang ba snying po don gyi rgyu las //
NG0456:94: rgyud kyi gtad rgya bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o ///
NG0456:95: / ye shes 'khor lo gsang ba'i snying po don gyi rgyud ces bya ba //
NG0456:96: la zlo ba chen po man ngag gi rgyab rtan rdzogs so //
